      I cannot possibly do this job.
  </td> </tr>
</table>
</p>

<p>
The denied statement may be about a possibility.

<table class="sentence">
  <tr class="jp"> <td>
      @HI{{@EM{{totemo}}@FG{{@KJ{{ego^noma}}:wareware}}ni@FG{{@KJ{{victory}}:ka}}chi@FG{{@KJ{{eye}}:me}}ha@EM{{nai}}.}}
  </td> </tr>
  <tr class="en"> <td>
      We have no chance of winning.
  </td> </tr>
</table>
</p>

<p>
The denied statement may also be about one's desire or willingness.

<table class="sentence">
  <tr class="jp"> <td>
      @HI{{son'na@FG{{@KJ{{dangerous}}:abunai}}tokoroniha@EM{{totemo}}@KJ{{child^submit}}wo@KJ{{going}}kaserare@EM{{nai}}.}}
  </td> </tr>
